title: Wuhan Residents Line Up for Hours to Buy Graves for Loved Ones
description: Residents in the Chinese city of Wuhan, where the coronavirus outbreak originated, have been forced to queue up for hours this week to organize proper burials for their loved ones who died as a result of the pandemic.
